   Heavyweight champion Mike Tyson will defend his
title against Razor Ruddock and James ``Buster'' Douglas in coming
months, a spokesman for promoter Don King said.
   Ruddock, ranked second by the World Boxing Council, has accepted
a million-dollar offer to fight Tyson, Al Braverman said Wednesday.
