<TEXT>
   Domestic automakers were scheduled to produce
198,219 cars and light trucks this week, up from last week's
183,292, Ward's Automotive Reports said Thursday.
   This week's production is higher than the same week a year ago,
in which 182,212 cars and light trucks were produced, the trade
journal said.
